{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be futuristic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Anya Sharma - Futuristic Artist</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0a192f; /* Dark blue */\n            --secondary-color: #00aaff; /* Bright blue */\n            --text-color: #ccd6f6; /* Light blue text */\n            --background-color: #050a17; /* Very dark blue */\n            --accent-color: #303040; /* Darker accent */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 170, 255, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin: 0;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--secondary-color), 0 0 20px var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        section:nth-child(odd) {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .artwork {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 170, 255, 0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .artwork:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 170, 255, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .artwork img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 300px; /* Fixed height for consistency */\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n            filter: brightness(90%); /* Slightly darker image */\n            transition: filter 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .artwork:hover img {\n            filter: brightness(110%);\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info {\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info h3 {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .artwork-info .tech-stack {\n            font-size: 0.8em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        /* Animation */\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% {\n                transform: scale(1);\n                opacity: 0.8;\n            }\n            50% {\n                transform: scale(1.05);\n                opacity: 1;\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: scale(1);\n                opacity: 0.8;\n            }\n        }\n\n        .animated-text {\n            animation: pulse 3s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-family: 'Roboto Mono', monospace;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            section h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .gallery {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n            .artwork-info {\n                padding: 15px;\n            }\n            .artwork-info h3 {\n                font-size: 1.3em;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            section {\n                padding: 40px 15px;\n            }\n            section h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .artwork img {\n                height: 250px;\n            }\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1 class=\"animated-text\">ANYA SHARMA</h1>\n            <p>Digital Sculptor & Generative Artist</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About</h2>\n            <p>Exploring the intersection of human creativity and algorithmic processes. My work delves into the ethereal beauty of the digital realm, crafting intricate forms and emergent patterns.</p>\n            <p>Utilizing cutting-edge technologies to visualize abstract concepts and future aesthetics.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Portfolio</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/0a192f/00aaff?text=ChronoSculpt\" alt=\"ChronoSculpt\">\n                    <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                        <h3>ChronoSculpt</h3>\n                        <p>A generative sculpture exploring the passage of time through fluid dynamics.</p>\n                        <p class=\"tech-stack\">Python, Processing, GLSL</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/0a192f/00aaff?text=NebulaBloom\" alt=\"NebulaBloom\">\n                    <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                        <h3>NebulaBloom</h3>\n                        <p>An interactive installation simulating the birth and decay of cosmic entities.</p>\n                        <p class=\"tech-stack\">Three.js, WebGL, React</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/0a192f/00aaff?text=QuantumEchoes\" alt=\"QuantumEchoes\">\n                    <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                        <h3>QuantumEchoes</h3>\n                        <p>Abstract visualization of quantum entanglement principles.</p>\n                        <p class=\"tech-stack\">Blender, Houdini, Cycles</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x300/0a192f/00aaff?text=CrystallineMind\" alt=\"CrystallineMind\">\n                    <div class=\"artwork-info\">\n                        <h3>CrystallineMind</h3>\n                        <p>Digital artwork representing the complex architecture of artificial intelligence.</p>\n                        <p class=\"tech-stack\">AI Art Generator, Photoshop</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Contact</h2>\n            <p>Interested in collaboration or commissions? Reach out.</p>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Signal</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2077 Anya Sharma. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Designed with <span style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\">&#9883;</span> & <span style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\">Code</span></p>\n            <p>\n                <a href=\"#\">LinkedIn</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\">Twitter</a> |\n                <a href=\"#\">ArtStation</a>\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JavaScript for potential future enhancements\n        document.querySelectorAll('.contact-form button').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', (event) => {\n                event.preventDefault();\n                alert('Message sent! (Simulated)');\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}